latestIgtvVideos.title: Acne battle with Ageless Clinic!
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I’ve been waiting for months to share this video with you’ll and it’s taken me A LOT of courage to do so. My acne journey is probably the thing I’m most insecure about, till today. I dealt with unbelievable amounts of anxiety and depression due to this. I’ve wanted to speak about what I went through so you all know that you’ll aren’t alone in this! I want to be able to help you’ll and give you the guidance I never got. It’s taken me almost 6 years to speak on this but better late than never! This is not for the purposes of a paid promotion or an advertisement. This is me being as transparent and raw with you guys as I can. @theagelessclinic genuinely changed my life and I am grateful to Dr Harshana for it every single day! If you’ll have any questions or anything at all please don’t hesitate to contact me. Also, everything I’ve said in this video is true - it is not scripted in any way.
